Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该说过了 萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:02:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Melanie Square」里不需要烈性毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.44,0:02:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一等 托尼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有办法 本大哥非要我把东西卖掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管你个人的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我斯通家族的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不守我规矩的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.14,0:02:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是总统还是第一夫人我都不放过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此打住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚特大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙由我带走 没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是老样子那么守旧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今时今日 在洛杉矶还不接受毒品的黑帮也就只有这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望「Melanie Square」能够成为一个正规的娱乐场所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还没有堕落到为了赚钱 而要违背信念的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说大话了 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:03:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子又没满头大汗地努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话还真是刺耳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「石头脑袋」托尼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄克 你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然跑过来真是抱歉 托尼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾娃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来街区看电影的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你没忘记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天要一起去游乐园哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我当然记得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸怎么可能忘记和狄克一起玩的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.52,0:03:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那混蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多做个了断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们感受一下 不听话会有何下场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:03:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦肯宁小姐 我是理查德·哈林顿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我想从您那里得到一个满意的答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于条件 我们将做出最大程度的让步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 这条件不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的回答不变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别总让我重复
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Melanie Square」是我们家族的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在这里的家伙 在这里挣钱的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会出卖他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 你快滚回去告诉你们的老大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你想要吃颗子弹 冷冰冰地回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你们还不清楚我们「Inferno」的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:05:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们再等3天 这是你们最后的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信您会改变主意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托尼·斯通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 托尼 那家伙如此有恃无恐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是虚张声势也让人怪不舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁兹 罗布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细地清查一下「Inferno」的背景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为他们只是普通的新兴组织
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使暂时封住了对方的武器 也不代表战斗结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的你根本是束手无策
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经可以针锋相对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有个好教练
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你可以去完成两个任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情到我家里去说 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是麦肯宁小姐的家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于没有家人的单身人士而言有些过于宽敞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 今天丽兹因为其他任务也被抽调出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事不宜迟 请告诉我任务的内容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个任务 今晚请你成为我的护卫陪我聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了吧 丽兹不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这里有万全的安保
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算是走个形式 我还是希望能有人陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么像你这般的高层 却总是只有一名保镖？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还需要其他人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是第二个任务 去监视某对母子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 如果是命令的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行 你不是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一定要去监视 其中有何意义 不问可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:09:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法查清「Inferno」的全貌？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在各地的情报贩子和店员之间打听消息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但获取的情报都是零零散散的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说他们与贝洛提奥家族有染
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又蹦出来个斯尔范德斯家族的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 也出现了「Bloodies」的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全搞不清楚状况…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁兹 你小子从什么时候起变得就只能搞到这种虚假情报？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 安顿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的确有认真调查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Inferno」的短期崛起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丰富的手段 不露身份的干部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及鲁兹等人的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整合起来思考的话 就得出答案了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是横跨西海岸各个家族的特殊组织
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙之所以会有恃无恐也是因为有足够的势力撑腰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想要存活下来 唯有向「Inferno」摇尾示好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很清楚这点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BOSS 如此一来「Melanie Square」就会被他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管对方是什么来头 我们怎么能背叛街区的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安顿 马上去安排一个与「Inferno」接触的聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要提出条件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「让你们的BOSS出席」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 你该不会是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和他…谈判谈判
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据他们组织的体系来看 真正的BOSS是不会出席的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足够向他们挑衅了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如此一来 他们一定会展开报复的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 不光是街区 就连您的家人也会陷入危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要死守到底
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那帮家伙知道他们要吞并的对手不好惹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是说根据对方的态度 要将那对母子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 即使如此…你也会接受吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这并不是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的回答是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要融入羊群 就要披上羊皮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒数第五位从你身边走过的人的特征是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20多岁的白人男子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴着道奇队的帽子 穿着黑色衬衫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.99,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,400)}<道奇队>：美国棒球大联盟 洛杉矶道奇队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据他打手机的样子看来 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他与朋友走散 正在寻找碰头地点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使披上羊皮 也不要忘记狼的嗅觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是你教给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买给他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么狄克 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托尼 务必小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安顿大哥说一切准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扮得这么帅 今天你又要搞什么花样？ 石头脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚特大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这与你无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住了 别做危害市民的勾当
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然到时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别墅那边 阿贝里与巴克等人已经做好万全的防备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜的那里可谓是洛杉矶最为安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Inferno」呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给麦肯宁小姐处理没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.52,0:14:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后的事情也由我来出面处理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你的体谅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为负责这片地区的我 心情难免有些复杂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想通过不开战的方式 让「Inferno」得到「Melanie Square」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 麦肯宁小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有两张王牌的话 基本就可以锁定胜局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗布传来了消息 集会马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前为止 这周围没有什么异常情况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要今晚不发生情况 我们就赢定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:16:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人意外 「Inferno」的干部中竟然有像你这样漂亮的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让诸位吃惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会只是个花瓶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该有叫你们带BOSS过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不敢自称是「Inferno」的No.1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过关于这次的谈判 我可以全权处理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此 请你们避免无礼的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃「Melanie Square」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您以为就凭这一句话我们就会收手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这笔人情 我一定会还上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的黑帮义气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无需这样 我们只想要「Melanie Square」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街区里都是一些被从其他地方赶出来 上不了台面的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一群无法在其他任何家族地盘上生活的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他们就是我们的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能背叛家人 否则就不合情理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「守旧的石头脑袋」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是人如其名呢 托尼·斯通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真正的家人受到了危险 你还能这么说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做的结局 你们也将会失去一切 没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.34,0:17:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再问您一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够将「Melanie Square」让给「Inferno」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊「Phantom」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下 是狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反击 干掉对方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei 开始工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ BOSS平安吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈判决裂 BOSS和安顿大哥倒是平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但罗布和鲁兹…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:18:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 大姐先和狄克待在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群不得了的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Inferno」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄克 你还没睡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 游乐园的哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾娃 艾娃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.72,0:23:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为道具 身为装置
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只要行使机能便好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:14.00,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}karma
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.05,0:00:31.46,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}何度も同じことの繰り返しの中を堕ちていっては
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:34.40,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}karma
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:38.67,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}この身は螺旋のよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:52.29,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}生まれ変わってもなお彷徨い続けている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:56.60,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}Ah～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.65,0:01:01.25,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}ブーエー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:05.75,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}安らかに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:10.24,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}ブーエー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:26.25,*OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}終わりにしよう　己の業で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:14.00,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.05,0:00:31.46,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}在无数回相同的重复中渐渐堕落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:34.40,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:38.67,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}此身就如螺旋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:52.29,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}即使重获新生 依然彷徨如故
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.65,0:01:01.25,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}安睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:05.75,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}安详地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:10.24,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}安睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:26.25,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}以吾之手 让一切落幕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:22:00.00,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}蛇に魅入られたら　真っ逆さまに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:03.42,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}墜ちよ　蛇の道深く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:06.50,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}憎しみはたわわに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:11.62,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}虚実は花と咲き乱れ実る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:17.05,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}夢の瑕疵の　唾棄すべき腑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.60,0:22:26.21,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}手をかけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:29.51,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}命を以て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:38.18,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}蒼白に開く指　まみえる前に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:44.14,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}もしもおもえが　暗殺者ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:50.55,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}迷い　嫉み　打ち砕くことができようか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:52.84,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悶絶せよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.77,0:23:00.30,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}堕落するときは　いっそ見事に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:03.76,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}血を吐き　毒に塗れ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:06.90,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}奈落へと向かわん
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:11.95,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}其処でしか見えない天を仰ぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:14.57,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}灼け爛れてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.57,0:23:17.75,*ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}明日を嗤えよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:22:00.00,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一旦被蛇所魅惑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:03.42,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}便会直直坠入蛇道深处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:06.50,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}憎恶累累不堪重负
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:11.62,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}虚实如鲜花遍地绽放结实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:17.05,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}却是梦的瑕疵 遭人唾弃的脏腑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.60,0:22:26.21,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}搭上这双手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:29.51,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}赌上这条命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:38.18,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}即将面对时 苍白地打开手指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:44.14,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}如果你是暗杀者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:50.55,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}是否就能粉碎迷惑心 嫉妒心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:52.84,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}痛苦昏厥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.77,0:23:00.30,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}当堕落之时 不如彻底点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:03.76,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}口吐鲜血 身涂剧毒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.76,0:23:06.90,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}向着地狱直奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:11.95,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}仰望在地狱才能一见的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:14.57,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}身形渐渐灼烧溃烂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.57,0:23:17.75,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}对未来嗤笑不已
